  <body>
    <p id="p_xfy_bgk_54b">To sort rows in a table, select the entire table (or specific rows) and use the
          <uicontrol><image href="../img/Sort16.png"/>Sort</uicontrol> action from the main toolbar
      or the contextual menu. This opens the <uicontrol>Sort</uicontrol> dialog box.</p>
    <p id="p_yfy_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="fig_zfy_bgk_54b">
        <title>Sort Dialog Box</title>
