    </p>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/sort-dialog-intro-para" id="p_agy_bgk_54b"/>
    <note id="note_bgy_bgk_54b">When you invoke the sorting operation over an entire table, the <uicontrol>Selected
        rows</uicontrol> option is disabled.</note>
